</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h4 id="剑指-offer-07-重建二叉树" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#剑指-offer-07-重建二叉树" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/zhong-jian-er-cha-shu-lcof/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">剑指 Offer 07. 重建二叉树<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h4>
<div class="language-cpp line-numbers-mode" data-ext="cpp"><pre v-pre class="language-cpp"><code><span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Solution</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
<span class="token keyword">public</span><span class="token operator">:</span>
